剩都幫啲大粒換機 買啲唔等駛嘢俾高層用嚟擦鞋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"反而通常都bid 多咗錢先，用淨就買週邊設備"},{"pid":"5541274aa1970e9dba672dd5a2ad6d1cc20ac586","tid":2508831,"uid":53959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"黑境：外行人管內行人，你識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1174558ae7df2b2ee8de27c85f94b465ec4dcc9b","tid":2508831,"uid":181747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"今次會唔會話審計署唔識cash flow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}